### AYYUAZ.APP JWT Authentication Debug Tests

@host = https://localhost:7038
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api

### 1. Health Check (Should work without authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Login with Admin user (Get JWT token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "Admin045@gmail.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### 3. Test About endpoint without token (Should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/about

### 4. Test About endpoint with token (Replace YOUR_TOKEN with actual token from step 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/about
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Test Protected About endpoint - Create About (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/about
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test About - JWT Debug",
    "description": "This is a test about entry to verify JWT authentication is working correctly."
}

### 6. Test token validation directly
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/validate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "YOUR_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### 7. Get current user info
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE